### 5. Add CLI override flags
For one-off behavior changes without editing config:

```bash
# Disable all self-healing for this invocation
rch --no-self-healing hook

# Or specifically:
rch --no-hook-auto-start hook

# Daemon-side:
rchd --no-hook-install
```

