### 6. Environment Variables Summary

| Variable | Values | Default | Effect |
|----------|--------|---------|--------|
| `RCH_NO_SELF_HEALING` | 0, 1, true, false | unset | Master disable for all self-healing |
| `RCH_HOOK_STARTS_DAEMON` | 0, 1, true, false | 1 | Hook auto-starts daemon |
| `RCH_DAEMON_INSTALLS_HOOKS` | 0, 1, true, false | 1 | Daemon auto-installs hooks |
| `RCH_DAEMON_START_TIMEOUT` | seconds | 3 | Max wait for daemon start |
| `RCH_AUTO_START_COOLDOWN` | seconds | 30 | Min time between auto-starts |
| `RCH_SELF_HEALING_LOG_LEVEL` | debug/info/warn/error | info | Log verbosity |

